descp2: An integer or tuple/list of 3 integers, specifying the strides of the convolution along the depth, height   and width. Can be a single integer to specify the same value for all spatial dimensions. Specifying any stride value != 1 is incompatible with specifying any `dilation_rate` value != 1.
